-- ELECTIONS -- 1990; CALIFORNIA -- ELECTIONS -- 1990; WHITE HOUSE; 
PRESIDENTIAL AIDES; POLITICAL AIDES; SUNUNU, JOHN H; UNITED STATES -- BUDGET; 
FAZIO, VIC; DEMOCRATIC PARTY; LEADERSHIP; QUAYLE, DAN; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN 
RELATIONS -- JAPAN; AKIHITO (EMPEROR OF JAPAN); SOUTER, DAVID H; SENATE 
JUDICIARY COMMITTEE (U.S.) 
</P>
