lost 20% of his net worth. . . . Along with the shirt off his back and the rest 
of the clothes he came in with -- which the Sheriff's Department misplaced -- 
the former head of Irvine's Lincoln Savings &amp; Loan had $25 in his wallet 
when he arrived -- but only $20 when he left. . . . No word from Keating on 
where the money went. Dan Weikel and Kris Lindgren 
